        <AnswerBlock
          answer="Pindi Sahota is an independent kitchen fitter serving Henley-in-Arden, Warwickshire, and the surrounding Forest of Arden — covering B95 and the villages of Beaudesert, Ullenhall, Tanworth-in-Arden, Lapworth, and beyond. With 30 years of experience fitting kitchens in period properties, rural homes, and farmhouse conversions, he provides a fixed-price quote after a £195 pre-installation survey, credited back in full on booking."
