      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Areas of the Arden Region Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi covers Henley-in-Arden and the whole of the surrounding B95 area, as well as the adjacent villages and rural areas within the Forest of Arden. Key locations include:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Henley-in-Arden &amp; Surrounds</h3>
