          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Rural &amp; Remote Properties</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li>Farmhouses and barn conversions in the Arden area</li>
              <li>Rural detached homes on unmarked lanes and farm tracks</li>
              <li>Properties without a conventional street address are no problem — call to confirm</li>
